WORKING in OSX 10.6, 10.5, 10.4 as an i686 executable

install cmake

checkoput the 2.3 branch of opencv

In opencv 2.3 ccmake, set arch to i686, no shared libs, no docs, no python support, no examples, min target of 10.4, no cuda, no tiff, build 3rd party, build carbon and extra compiler directives to  
-fno-stack-protector

configure then generate inside of ccmake

Compile: make -j8
install: sudo make install

In the ImageMatcher folder, simply run make